definitions.definition: Two people who work or collaborate together as partners; especially, those who perform music together.
Any cocktail consisting of a spirit and a liqueur .
A meal with two paired components.
examples: The duo of pork consisted of a smoked sausage and a shoulder joint.

definitions.definition: A song in two parts; a duet .
